Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.17,0:00:07.98,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本片轻描淡写地讲述了南家三姐妹平凡的日常生活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:10.35,title2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要过度期待
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5  6  7  8  9…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.23,0:00:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保坂  保坂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.18,0:00:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝天椒要切成丝放进去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.65,0:00:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多炒会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？怎么了  速水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.99,0:00:32.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保坂你想继续做料理到什么时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.93,0:00:33.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多此一问
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人只要活着就少不了吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.17,0:00:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不做料理之日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.39,0:00:40.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是死亡之时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.61,0:00:43.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.84,0:00:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.75,0:00:50.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是可以考虑偶尔用些其它方法来引春香注意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.33,0:00:51.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它的方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比方说  你看  那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.94,0:00:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10  11  12  13
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.42,0:01:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14  15  16  17…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.19,0:01:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？是16
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.46,0:01:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.38,0:01:05.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于这个越来越冷的季节是必不可少的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始努力说不定能赶在圣诞节之前送出去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.84,0:01:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:18.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便一提从今年的流行和我的喜好上来说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.16,0:01:21.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推荐这种感觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.66,0:01:25.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  加油试试看吧  保坂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.05,0:01:28.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寒假到来之前完成它…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:29.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了南春香开始做料理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.49,0:01:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技术上的确进步了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:39.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我还没有让她笑过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前连话都没有说过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:47.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不成熟的双手不论做什么都不成的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.26,0:01:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来我令南春香展开笑容的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.69,0:01:53.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时再开始织东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:58.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让她和女儿们得到温暖的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:02:01.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香说过喜欢织的东西哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.57,0:02:05.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那么从今天开始我也喜欢织东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,31  诶？  我说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.38,0:02:13.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意  继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:16.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.43,0:02:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,32  33  34  35  36  37…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.24,0:02:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在编织的时候最重要的是平常心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.19,0:02:31.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,焦躁了会织错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.72,0:02:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用力过大会网眼会缠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适当休息下  做些伸展运动之类的悠闲地织吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.48,0:02:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之享受才是织东西的精髓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.19,0:02:47.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？网眼多了一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:03:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个网眼用力不均宽度就会变吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:01.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真深奥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:05.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,55  56  57  58…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.97,0:03:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的圣诞节可以期待了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:42.92,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(700,310)}圣夜、神仙下凡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:46.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:48.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:52.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希穿了新大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:55.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉  让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.54,0:04:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  刚到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.95,0:04:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.06,0:04:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:06.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以为变冷了  不过今天更冷了一个级别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:08.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  特别冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.90,0:05:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子的围巾毛绒绒的感觉很厚很暖和  是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  这个很暖和所以很中意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希的大衣感觉也很暖和真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:23.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,注意到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.85,0:05:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是新买的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一不小心就买了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.52,0:05:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很适合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:40.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希问问题的意图很容易懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:45.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子能理解我问题的意图真是帮了大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.45,0:05:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？啊  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.90,0:05:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.94,0:05:53.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.23,0:05:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在有点烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真少见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子  想问你一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.48,0:06:07.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:11.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡味的牛奶可可和加了过多的乳脂的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个更好些？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.05,0:06:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得哪个更好些？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:23.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可可？咖啡？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为选哪个而烦恼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像不太对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.60,0:06:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在打比方？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淡味牛奶可可和放了过多的乳脂的咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道淡加点就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.71,0:06:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一边只要再加些咖啡就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.54,0:06:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过还要加热水和糖…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把放多了的味道调回去会很难
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:50.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得可可更好些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然吗  淳子也这样想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.23,0:06:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然真希今天早上穿的大衣是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.95,0:06:59.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「淡味的牛奶可可」色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:06:59.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:06.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选哪个都是不对的么…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.81,0:07:13.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在叫我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.59,0:07:16.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了保坂学长
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:18.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淳子  你怎样想？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.32,0:07:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.68,0:07:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个到底是重复了呢还是没重复呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:28.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不明白意图的二选一问题啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会不会选哪个都是不对的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:34.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个重复了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.82,0:07:35.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:37.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有重复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.84,0:07:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能两个都不是呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.60,0:07:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许是正确答案
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得真希新大衣的颜色和南春香大衣的颜色重复了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:53.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本身并不是问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:55.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种意义上说答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:07:58.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是少见的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.12,0:08:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复了也正常
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那拿铁咖啡的颜色进入到视线的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会困惑也是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.57,0:08:10.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.03,0:08:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.00,0:08:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无处可去的心情该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无计可施啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:19.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要问为什么  无处可去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.19,0:08:23.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些问题似乎多想无用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:27.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱进行时里说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:31.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女生的价值是由被男生告白的次数决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.67,0:08:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说那句话的是竞争对手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:36.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且在那之后被甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.29,0:08:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管这样我觉得还是有一番道理的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何内田  最近很受欢迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:43.02,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想也无济于事的话还是不要去想了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:41.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没受欢迎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.41,0:08:42.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我怎样才能受欢迎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.36,0:08:45.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  淳子  老实说你很受欢迎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.78,0:08:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:48.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？果然很受欢迎吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.52,0:08:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:51.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是有受欢迎秘诀吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.77,0:08:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样才能受欢迎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:54.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:57.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:59.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样才能受欢迎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:02.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我什么都没有想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂内田  什么都不想就会受欢迎哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？夏奈那种事情可能吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:12.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你们在说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.50,0:09:15.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来淳子是被称为魔女的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定拥有魔法之类的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:20.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱的魔法使？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:24.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是一个说害羞的话也不脸红的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.94,0:09:25.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那种事情  淳子老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我受欢迎的秘诀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:32.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请告诉我恋爱的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:35.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  那…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上皇家奶茶色的大衣之类的会好一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:45.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.04,0:09:52.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  有皇家奶茶色的大衣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.13,0:09:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  借我皇家奶茶色的大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.66,0:09:56.87,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我什么脑筋都没动
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.84,0:09:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不借
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.10,0:10:00.55,zhushi2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这样就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.53,0:09:58.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  好嘛拜托了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.84,0:10:00.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有给你用的大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.66,0:10:03.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么啊千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:07.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上了春香的皇家奶茶色的大衣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就受欢迎了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.05,0:10:10.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:13.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把别人认成了南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:17.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天空也在嘲笑我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:19.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.41,0:10:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.27,0:10:24.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到下的这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:26.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:29.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓纯白就是那样了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.61,0:10:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  掀开窗帘就是满面的银色世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我醒来的时候窗帘已经被妹妹拉开了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经相当的兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.53,0:10:43.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跳出窗外被雪埋上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的妹妹已经这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.39,0:10:49.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我也像她那么年轻也会跳出去被雪埋上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话真想雪再积得深一些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.09,0:10:55.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话就可以堆雪屋了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:10:58.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪屋？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.04,0:11:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温馨的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.91,0:11:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还会下雪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.13,0:11:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,36.8度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低烧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:24.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:27.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美  哪里不舒服么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:30.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些乏力  量了体温
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.48,0:11:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过只是低烧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:36.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香学姐也来量体温？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:38.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些乏力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然变冷了  很怕感冒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.46,0:11:44.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上的雪也很大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:48.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思我先离开了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.43,0:11:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.22,0:11:58.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在走廊上干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问干什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.47,0:12:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…还是扣上比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:17.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才量体温之后忘记扣上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.76,0:12:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你看到了么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:35.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然用这种坚定又纯真的少年的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.56,0:12:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮  简直就是满面的纯白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:42.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别特地把颜色说出来啊  纯白什么的别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为打开着一下子就充满了视野
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是故意的…什么  兴…兴奋？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.62,0:12:54.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来软绵绵地非常柔软
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:56.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞扑上去一定很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:13:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞…飞扑什么的  就在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真危险
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.58,0:13:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是再年轻一些就会扑上去深埋进去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:09.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是有多大啊  不是跟我同岁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来还真可惜  能再大一点就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再大一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你也看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.54,0:13:24.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.76,0:13:29.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,36.5也算正常体温吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.82,0:13:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还是有些乏力  不过加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:37.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.80,0:13:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  我说  夏树看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了…还是说快要看到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.59,0:13:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是白茫茫的一片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.21,0:13:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的纯白色了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:13:59.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点也没在看！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:09.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明积了这么多雪  是没在看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.87,0:14:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:16.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仁美  在生什么气吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.39,0:14:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不为别的  都是因为夏树那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:23.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个差劲的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不揍他一顿就咽不下这口气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口被那家伙看了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:36.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是目不转睛的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.66,0:14:37.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.24,0:14:47.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…刚才…夏树他…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还用少年纯真的眼神说什么纯白很漂亮什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:53.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯白？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:58.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说他很兴奋什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:14:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兴奋…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:01.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还说看起来软绵绵很柔软的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想飞扑上去什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.47,0:15:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想飞扑上去？！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:09.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像还说要是再年轻一些就危险了什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说我已经老了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.19,0:15:17.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至还说要是再大一点就好了  太差劲了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再大一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
