Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.58,0:22:53.45,EDJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\an8}神は舞い降りる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
