Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.58,0:22:53.45,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}神会从天而降
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.74,0:22:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你的这份感情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.04,0:22:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是喜爱也不是喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:22:53.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找不到更切合的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.30,0:22:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今晚  今夜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.19,0:23:01.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了与你相符的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.27,0:23:05.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终极的爱  无尽的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那已经超越了人的领域
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.12,0:23:10.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  南春香
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.09,0:23:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说你就是…没错！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.12,0:23:18.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女神哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
